        </p>

        <h5>1. Information We Collect</h5>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Customer Profiles:</strong> Name, email address, and loyalty program details.</li>
            <li><strong>Orders:</strong> Product purchases, order history, and delivery preferences.</li>
            <li><strong>Files & Documents:</strong> Contracts or forms you upload to our system.</li>
            <li><strong>Images:</strong> Product images uploaded for catalog or gallery purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h5>2. How We Use Your Information</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and improve our services.</li>
            <li>To store and manage customer profiles.</li>
            <li>To process orders and track deliveries.</li>
            <li>To maintain a record of contracts and product media.</li>
        </ul>

